response.overview: After the death of his mother, a young boy calls a radio station in an attempt to set his father up on a date. Talking about his father’s loneliness soon leads to a meeting with a young female journalist, who has flown to Seattle to write a story about the boy and his father.
response.tagline: What if someone you never met, someone you never saw, someone you never knew was the only someone for you?
response.title: Sleepless in Seattle
